into an img that is rendered by
[http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex](http://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?%5CDelta).

Example Here:

E=mc\^2

N(x)=\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2
\\pi}}\\int\_{-\\infty}\^{x}e\^{-\\frac{z\^2}{2}}dz

